OL,7,F"Not once in the last 30 years had mum
OL,8,Fpersonally sought any kind of
OL,9,Femergency NHS care, that is until the
OL,10,Ftragic circumstances we have re-lived
OL,11,Fhere today," her son John said.
OL,13,F"And tragic is truly what it is. It is
OL,14,Fbeyond belief quite how
OL,15,Fcatastrophically she was failed not by
OL,16,Fone individual but by the NHS trust.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
