OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,F"Life will not be the same without mum
OL,8,Fand we cannot bring her back, but we
OL,9,Fwould be failing as a family if we
OL,10,Fdidn't highlight how much room for
OL,11,Fimprovement there is at the Royal
OL,12,FBlackburn Hospital emergency
OL,13,Fdepartment."
OL,15,FOn that night, the accident and
OL,16,Femergency department had been
OL,17,Fcategorised as 'over capacity and over-
OL,18,Fstretched' an hour before Pat arrived.
OL,19,FThere were more than 90 patients
OL,20,Fwaiting to be seen.
