OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FAccompanied by her son John, she was
OL,8,Ftaken to the resus area as A&E buckled
OL,9,Funder overwhelming pressure. Barely
OL,10,Ffour hours later Pat was dead.
OL,12,FAn inquest heard how the retired nurse
OL,13,Fwho devoted her life to the NHS would
OL,14,Fprobably have survived if medics
OL,15,Fhadn't checked the wrong patient's
OL,16,Fnotes which had a 'do not resuscitate'
OL,17,Forder in place.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/15
