OL,7,FThe court was told how Pat was taken
OL,8,Fto Royal Blackburn Hospital by
OL,9,Fambulance with a suspected bowel
OL,10,Fobstruction on 19 September.
OL,12,FAs she waited to be seen, she told
OL,13,FJohn that she needed the toilet.
OL,15,FJohn asked for a commode but at least
OL,16,Ftwo nurses failed to return with one
OL,17,Fand after waiting for a 'significant
OL,18,Fperiod' John ended up wheeling Pat to
OL,19,Fthe toilet himself.
