OL,7,FJohn regularly asked his mum if she
OL,8,Fwas ok but on asking a third time he
OL,9,Freceived no response. Staff then
OL,10,Fentered the toilet and found Pat
OL,11,Fslumped against the wall with dark
OL,12,Ffluid coming out of her mouth.
OL,14,FA healthcare assistant was first on
OL,15,Fthe scene and, after noting Pat had no
OL,16,Fpulse, CPR was started which quickly
OL,17,Fresulted in a return of spontaneous
OL,18,Fcirculation.
