OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FPat, who was was born in Salford and
OL,8,Flived in Rawtenstall, was then taken
OL,9,Finto a room but her heart stopped
OL,10,Fbeating a second time.
OL,12,FNurses went to check the notes and
OL,13,Freturned to inform John that she had a
OL,14,F'Do Not Resuscitate' in place and she
OL,15,Fpassed away at 9.35pm - less than four
OL,16,Fhours after she had arrived at the
OL,17,Fhospital.
