OL,7,FAs John sat with his mother after she
OL,8,Fhad been pronounced dead he was
OL,9,Fvisited by a senior nurse who informed
OL,10,Fhim of the mistake. The inquest, at
OL,11,FAccrington Town Hall, heard that the
OL,12,Fpatient whose notes were confused for
OL,13,FPat's was a 90-year-old man.
