OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, tragically and
OL,8,Fcatastrophically these were not Pat's
OL,9,Frecords; they belonged to an entirely
OL,10,Fdifferent patient who was male and in
OL,11,Fhis 90s; characteristics which Pat
OL,12,Fvery clearly did not share," Area
OL,13,FCoroner Kate Bisset said. "It was
OL,14,Fquickly realised that a DNR was not in
OL,15,Fplace however, tragically, it was too
OL,16,Flate."
