OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FIn his statement read out during the
OL,8,Finquest, Pat's son John said: "I know
OL,9,Fthat our mum will have been horrified
OL,10,Fby how the system she gave her life to
OL,11,Ffailed her at her time of greatest
OL,12,Fneed.
OL,14,F"It is beyond belief the catastrophic
OL,15,Fway in which she was failed, not only
OL,16,Fby one individual but by doctors who
OL,17,Fhave sworn the Hippocratic oath to do
OL,18,Fno harm and our mum paid the ultimate
OL,19,Fprice."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
