OL,7,FDr Alabood, who admitted that it is
OL,8,Fprobable that Pat would have been
OL,9,Fresuscitated had medics attempted to
OL,10,Fdo so, was asked by the coroner if
OL,11,Fthere was anything else he wanted to
OL,12,Fsay regarding Pat's admission to A&E
OL,13,Fto which he replied: "It was
OL,14,Funfortunate".
OL,16,FThe coroner then interjected: "Well it
OL,17,Fwas beyond unfortunate wasn't it. It
OL,18,Fwas catastrophic."
