OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that as he left the
OL,8,Fhospital Pat's son John bumped into
OL,9,Fthe paramedic who had brought his mum
OL,10,Fin. John informed the paramedic that
OL,11,FPat had died. "He was totally stunned;
OL,12,Fhe couldn't believe she had died,"
OL,13,FJohn said.
OL,15,FSeveral systemic changes have been
OL,16,Fimplemented since Pat's death after
OL,17,Fconcerns were highlighted during an
OL,18,Finternal investigation. These include
OL,19,Flimiting the number of patients each
OL,20,Fnurse looks after to five and
OL,21,Freactivating a DNR every three months.
