OL,7,FThe coroner concluded that Pat would
OL,8,Fnot have died when she did had it not
OL,9,Fbeen for the mistakes and,
OL,10,Fsignificantly, made a ruling of
OL,11,Fneglect. She added: "I am satisfied
OL,12,Fthat Mrs Dawson would not have died,
OL,13,Fat that point, if the care she had
OL,14,Freceived had been different."
